   @{b}comfortably starting files@{ub} with various applications, the

   @{" + " SYSTEM "run <>NIL: ${RefTable/File-Starter}"} EASys! FileStarter: @{i}${RefTable/File-Starter}@{ui}


   (included with the EASys!_Plus package)

   (equals to the 'SendTo' Function of Win.95) Available for
   Registration fee.

   Have a 'SendTo' Menu configured with the ToolManager
   Menu-Enhancer and the EASys!-FileStarter. (sure, you may also use
   another WB-Menu-Enhancer)

   Now select a workbench-Icon, press the right Mouse-Button and
   choose 'Tools/SendTo...' the selected File will be passed to the

   EASys!-FileStarter

   and you will be presented a large user-customizable list of
   Apps/Tools which the file may be started with.
   Just doubleclick the desired entry!



